OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1783864145
OL,3,CIs stopping Haaland the key to England
OL,4,Csuccess?
OL,6,FIf England stop Erling Haaland they'll
OL,7,Fmake it to the semi-final. Is it
OL,8,Freally that simple?
OL,10,FWell, in a way it is. In any team
OL,11,Fsport, if you can ensure that your
OL,12,Fopponent's best players don't have an
OL,13,Fimpact then you're half way there.
OL,15,FSo are England equipped to do that?
OL,16,FWell they certainly have the insider
OL,17,Fknowledge because of course most of
OL,18,Fthem either play alongside him, or
OL,19,Fagainst him in the Premier League.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
