OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1783864145
OL,3,CIs stopping Haaland the key to England
OL,4,Csuccess?
OL,6,FHis teammates are John Stones, Marc
OL,7,FGuehi and Nico O'Reilly ` they watch
OL,8,Fand study him day in and day out at
OL,9,Fthe Etihad and will have passed on
OL,10,Fuseful intelligence to Thomas Tuchel.
OL,12,FAs for the defenders who've played
OL,13,Fagainst him. Ezri Konsa has faced him
OL,14,Ffive times for Aston Villa and Haaland
OL,15,Fhas only scored in one of those games.
OL,17,FDan Burn has kept Haaland quiet too.
OL,18,FThey have come up against each other
OL,19,Feight times in the Premier League and
OL,20,Fagain Haaland has only scored once.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
