CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1783864145
OL,3,CIs stopping Haaland the key to England
OL,4,Csuccess?
OL,6,FThe stats don't look so good though
OL,7,Fwhen it comes to Jordan Pickford in
OL,8,Fthe England goal.
OL,10,FHaaland has scored seven times in
OL,11,Ftheir six meetings. Although Pickford
OL,12,Fhas saved a Haaland penalty which may
OL,13,Fbe a useful psychological advantage if
OL,14,Fit comes to it.
OL,16,FOf course the best way to stop Erling
OL,17,FHaaland, is not great defending when
OL,18,Fhe's got the ball, but not allowing
OL,19,Fhim to get the ball in the first place.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/4
